@host = http://localhost:5104

### Initiate a transfer (atomic outbox write)
POST {{host}}/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "PL61109010140000071219812874",
  "toAccount": "PL27114020040000300201355387",
  "amount": 1500.00
}

### Get all transfers
GET {{host}}/transfers

### Check pending outbox messages
GET {{host}}/outbox/pending

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health
